## Formatting Rules

- Count every countable thing before recommending.
- Flag threshold violations against the cited source (Miller, Cowan, Iyengar,
  Sweller).
- Dominant-load type determines the cut strategy.
- Germane deficit means ADD, not cut.
- Tradeoffs always accompany cuts.
